The '''NoorderSoft Waterways Database''' is a [[georelational]] database that contains all data on inland waterways in [[Europe]], the [[United States]] and many other parts of the world. The database is maintained in order to allow logistic calculations and planning processes for inland [[Ship transport|waterways transport]], [[Inland port|inland shipping]] and [[boating|leisure boating]]. The database contains dimension data, distance data, communication data and operational data.

NoorderSoft is a company based in the Netherlands. It develops and produces voyage planners for inland shipping and other logistical software tools. The company maintains a range of dynamic data concerning the inland waterways network, such as obstruction tables, harmonized selections of Notices to Skippers and similar relevant data.

